 &  & \sigma_{r}
\end{smallmatrix}\right]=\left[\begin{smallmatrix}\frac{1}{\sigma_{1}}\\
 & \ddots\\
 &  & \frac{1}{\sigma_{r}}
\end{smallmatrix}\right]=\tilde{\Sigma}^{-1}
\]

\end_inset

